metadata.name: Butcher And Freaks
metadata.description:
I read somewhere that if the slaughterhouses were made of glass, of course it would be over  
Humans became vegetarians. Now imagine that you have entered a butcher shop, not one of those European butcher shops whose cleanliness is evident, but one of those suppliers that has more than one store like a small Auschwitz for cattle. Now you can come to the understanding that there are also showcases in the form of a chain of essences throughout your life .
